d\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"James and company will get a rematch with Serbia and\\u00a0two-time NBA MVP Nikola Joki\\u0107 in the semifinal.\", \"from\": 3971, \"to\": 4071, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3971, \"end\": 3976, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LeBron_James\", \"score\": 0.9999999999993179, \"rank\": 4.5068073344230153e-13, \"text\": \"James\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LeBron_James\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LeBron_James\"}, {\"begin\": 4013, \"end\": 4019, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Serbia_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9966904896784778, \"rank\": 0.0033084542607322966, \"text\": \"Serbia\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Serbia_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Serbia_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 4033, \"end\": 4040, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBA_Most_Valuable_Player_Award\", \"score\": 0.9999999998381099, \"rank\": 1.618931419726666e-10, \"text\": \"NBA MVP\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBA_Most_Valuable_Player_Award\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBA_Most_Valuable_Player_Award\"}, {\"begin\": 4041, \"end\": 4053, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nikola_Joki\\u0107\", \"score\": 0.9999999949416178, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Nikola Joki\\u0107\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nikola_Joki\\u0107\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nikola_Joki\\u0107\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The U.S. defeated Serbia in group play 110-84.\", \"from\": 4072, \"to\": 4118, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4090, \"end\": 4096, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Serbia_national_football_team\", \"sc