pain 4-2 to meet the Americans in the final.\", \"from\": 4324, \"to\": 4482, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4348, \"end\": 4355, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Germany_women's_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9999981995214576, \"rank\": 1.7997664995166846e-06, \"text\": \"Germany\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Germany_women's_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Germany_women's_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 4421, \"end\": 4427, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brazil_women's_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9999999998212843, \"rank\": 1.781638653311343e-10, \"text\": \"Brazil\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brazil_women's_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brazil_women's_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 4437, \"end\": 4442, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spain_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.7711296300173159, \"rank\": 0.29674794295330775, \"text\": \"Spain\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spain_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spain_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The two teams will meet for a chance at Olympic gold on Saturday.\", \"from\": 4484, \"to\": 4549, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Despite its four gold medals, the most of any team in the Olympics, the U.S. has missed out on the finals at the last two Olympic tournaments.\", \"from\": 4551, \"to\": 4693, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The U.S. was eliminated in the quarterfinals in 2016 in Rio and relegated to the bronze medal match at the Tokyo Games three years ago.But the U.S. now has a chance to reclaim the gold for the fifth time in USWNT history.\", \"from\": 4694, \"to\": 4915, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4750, \"end\": 4753, 