inal on Tuesday.\", \"from\": 6544, \"to\": 6774, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6658, \"end\": 6666, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9991846590865068, \"rank\": 0.0006370525248643413, \"text\": \"American\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 6667, \"end\": 6675, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\", \"score\": 0.9999643957842591, \"rank\": 3.560548323023385e-05, \"text\": \"Olympian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She beat opponent Meerim Zhumanazarova of Kyrgyzstan 3-0 to claim the top spot on the podium.\", \"from\": 6776, \"to\": 6869, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6794, \"end\": 6814, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Meerim_Zhumanazarova\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Meerim Zhumanazarova\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Meerim_Zhumanazarova\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Meerim_Zhumanazarova\"}, {\"begin\": 6818, \"end\": 6828, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kyrgyzstan\", \"score\": 0.9999999985944896, \"rank\": 1.1862119654316218e-09, \"text\": \"Kyrgyzstan\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kyrgyzstan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kyrgyzstan\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"According to USA Today, the win marked 41 consecutive victories for Elor at the international level.\", \"from\": 6870, \"to\": 6970, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6883, \"end\": 6892, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/USA_Today\", \"score\": 0.9994926639798786, \"rank\": 0.000507512062750696, \"text\": \"USA Today\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q11032\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/USA_Today\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/USA_Today\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This is not new territory for the promising young wrestler.\", \"from\": 6972, \"to\": 7031, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"She is a two-time World Champion in the women's 72 kg division and her gold medal in 2022 made her the youngest U.S. World Champion at just 18-years-old.\", \"from\": 7032, \"to\": 7185, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Romanian Prime Minister Marcel Ciolacu said Tuesday he will boycott theParis Olympics'closing ceremony over a scoring decision in the women's gymnastics floor final.\", \"from\": 7189, \"to\": 7354, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 7189, \"end\": 7212, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Prime_Minister_of_Romania\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Romanian Prime Minister\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Prime_Minister_of_Romania\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Prime_Minister_of_Romania\"}, {\"begin\": 7213, \"end\": 7227, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Marcel_Ciolacu\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Marcel Ciolacu\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Marcel_Ciolacu\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Marcel_Ciolacu\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Romanian gymnast\\u00a0Ana Barbosu\\u00a0had initially clinched the bronze medal for floor on Monday and began celebrating on the mat.\", \"from\": 7356, \"to\": 7478, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 7356, \"end\": 7364, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Romanian_language\", \"score\": 0.9822724492491907, \"rank\": 0.018035558905395228, \"text\": \"Romanian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Romanian_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Romanian_language\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But then U.S. coaches appealed to judges over Jordan Chiles' score, and a review resulted in a 0.1-point increase, which moved Chiles ahead of Barbosu for the bronze medal.\", \"from\": 7479, \"to\": 7651, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 7525, \"end\": 7538, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jordan_Chiles\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Jordan Chiles\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jordan_Chiles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jordan_Chiles\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Barbosu was then left off the podium.\", \"from\": 7653, \"to\": 7690, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"She was holding a Romanian flag when she looked up and saw the scoring change on the board.\", \"from\": 7691, \"to\": 7782, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 7709, \"end\": 7722, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Flag_of_Romania\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Romanian flag\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Flag_of_Romania\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Flag_of_Romania\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Just then, she dropped the flag, covered her face with her hands and walked away in tears.\", \"from\": 7783, \"to\": 7873, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"This is an excerpt from a report by Jackson Thompson.\", \"from\": 7875, \"to\": 7928, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 7911, \"end\": 7927, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jackson_Thompson\", \"score\": 0.9999706668926694, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Jackson Thompson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jackson_Thompson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jackson_Thompson\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Cole Hocker is going home with a gold medal after pulling off a huge upset to win the men's 1500-meter final, setting an Olympic record in the process.\", \"from\": 7930, \"to\": 8081, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 7930, \"end\": 7941, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cole_Hocker\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Cole Hocker\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", 